        .explanation
          p Select a color from the picker in order to determine whether it's considered light or dark using the different algorithms below. Text color will be opposite of the lightness test result.
          p You can also set the lightness treshold value for different results:
          form oninput="threshold.value=thresholdRange.value"
            input type="range" id="thresholdRange" name="thresholdRange" min="0.4" max="0.8" step="0.1" value="0.5"
